replies.author: 玩脱
replies.txt_content:
怪物萌化mod引起的客户端崩溃
删除怪物萌化mod即可解决

replies.author: Didiao0v0
replies.txt_content:
在服务器的config找到forge.cfg
打开后找到B:removeErroringEntities=false
改为
B:removeErroringEntities=true
